               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Malʾǝkta Ṗeṭros qadāmāwi "First Epistle of Peter" [1 Peter] (fols. 3ra-11ra)&#xD;
II) Malʾǝkta Ṗeṭros dāgǝmāwi "Second Epistle of Peter" [2 Peter] (fols. 11ra-15va)&#xD;
III) Malʾǝkta Yoḥannǝs qadāmāwi "First Epistle of John" [1 John] (fols. 15va-22va)&#xD;
IV) Malʾǝkta Yoḥannǝs dāgǝmāwi "Second Epistle of John" [2 John] (fols. 22va-23va)&#xD;
V) Malʾǝkta Yoḥannǝs śalǝsawi "Third Epistle of John" [3 John] (fols. 23va-24va)&#xD;
VI) Malʾǝkta Yāʿqob "Epistles of Jacob" [Jas.] (fols. 24va-30vb)&#xD;
VII) Malʾǝkta Yǝhuda "Epistle of Judah" [Jude] (fols. 30vb-32vb)&#xD;
VIII) Rāʾǝya Yoḥannǝs "Revelation of John" [Rev.] (fols. 33ra-62rb)&#xD;
IX) Gǝbra ḥawāryāt "Acts of the Apostles" [Acts] (fols. 63ra-129ra)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-2.</summary>
